## Coding Standards

| Standard | Rule |
|----------|------|
| Variable prefix | `mos_` for medical object storage variables |
| Constant prefix | `E_` for regulatory limits and constants |
| Function length | 40 lines maximum |
| Test coverage | 85% minimum |
| Branding in titles | `MedinovAI` (title case) |
| Branding in paths/IDs | `medinovai` (lowercase) |
| API response time | < 200ms P95 |
| Health endpoint | Every service must expose `GET /health` |

---

## Compliance Requirements

- **HIPAA:** PHI handling, BAA required for all external data partners
- **GDPR:** Right to erasure via consent cascade
- **21 CFR Part 11:** Electronic records, immutable audit trails, e-signatures
- **EU MDR:** Infrastructure supporting medical device software
- **FDA Class II:** Regulatory class for clinical decision support services

