## Service Discovery: `medinovai.manifest.yaml`

Every repo must have `medinovai.manifest.yaml` at its root:

```yaml
service:
  name: medinovai-{service-name}
  version: "1.0.0"
  tier: {0-4}
  category: {platform|security|clinical|ai-ml|integration|frontend|infrastructure}
  health_endpoint: /health
  port: {port}
  dependencies:
    - medinovai-{dependency-1}
  squad: {squad-name}

observability:
  log_level: 2
  sampling_rate: 0.5

deployment:
  dockerfile: Dockerfile
  port: {port}
  min_replicas: 1
  canary_enabled: false
```

The **Service Registry Agent** (in `medinovai-atlas-os`) reads these manifests across all repos via GitHub API and builds a live service map.

